						<summary>

						<p>On a Nāga-pillar set up before the temple of Bhīmēśvarasvāmi.</p>						

						<p>This is dated Śaka 1090, Vishnu Saṅkraṅti.</p>						

						<p>Records the construction of a temple for Bhīmēśvara and gift lands for burning a perpetual lamp at Pālaḍgu in Koṇḍapaḍumaṟa by Prōle-Reḍḍi, son of Guṇḍi-Raḍḍi of Vēṟuru, for the merit of his parents.</p>						

						</summary>
